The '''Rellekka Longhall Bar''' is a bar found in the [[Rellekka]] longhall. It sells two kinds of [[beer]] and [[Keg of beer|kegs of beer]]. Some NPCs located in the bar are the focus of the [[quest]] [[The Fremennik Trials]], in which the player must enlist the support of [[Manni the Reveller]] and begin the quest by talking to [[Brundt the Chieftain]].

The stage of this bar is used by players during The Fremennik Trials, where they play an instrument for progression of the quest.

[[Thora the Barkeep]] also resides in the bar, and sells two kinds of [[beer]] (one in a glass, one in a [[beer tankard|tankard]]) and a keg of beer.

